      private List<List<String>> getRecordsToPrintForToStringMethods(HashMap<AlignmentsCube.TestCaseMatcher,PrefixLookup> left, HashMap<AlignmentsCube.TestCaseMatcher,PrefixLookup> right, boolean printShort)
